  "description": [
    "PAGE FOUR Brewery Gulch Gazette 120 Nace Road Bisbee Arizona Phone HE 25333 1 Published Every Thursday GEORGE A BIDEAUX Editor and Publisher RAY HALVORSEN Manging Editor Notional Advertising Representative W N EWSPAPER REPRESENTATIVES INC New York Chicago Detroit Philadelphia This newspaper is a member of J Arizona Newspapers Association For greater Public Service NATION A I EDITORIAL vL I asoctlqn Subscription 250 per year by mail Entered as secondclass matter May 22 1931 at the post office at Bisbee Arizona under the act of March 3 1879 EDITORIAL SCIENCE AND THE GULCH We oldtimers in Brewery Gulch are going to sit back and see if the scientific work at Ft Huachuca can change us like they say it will We dont change easy The only digital com puter we ever needed to figure out our problems was the 10 fingers on our hands Life is seldom so complicated for us that we cant reason it out in a couple minutes Of course we know there is them that likes a complicated life and so we send our children to the Uiversity so they can learn about it Gives them a chance to make a free choice whether to mix"
  ],
